article_title: Man Found Dead in PCB Hotel, Police Investigating
article_text:
UPDATE 11:51 A.M.

Panama City Beach Police are investigating the death of 21-year old Coty Trenell Haywood of Perry, Florida.

A little after 8 a.m. Saturday police received a call of an unresponsive person in a hotel room at the Boardwalk Beach Resort.

When they arrived on scene they found Haywood dead.

No foul play is suspected at this time.

An autopsy is set for a later date.

--------------------------------------

Panama City Beach Police officials are investigating after they found a body Saturday morning in a hotel room at the Boardwalk Beach Resort.

We have a reporter on scene.

More details here on Newschannel 7 when they become available.

article_metadata.description: Panama City Beach Police have identified the man who was found dead Saturday morning in a hotel room at the Boardwalk Beach Resort.
